{"id": 58, "genre": 1000, "title": "处女座为什么这样红？", "description": "处女月到了，处女座的朋友们又到了舆论的风口浪尖！处女座作为星座界的五仁月饼，常年受到不公正的待遇。但是，随着许多公司以正（yíng）义（xiāo）为目的推出了“非处女座不招”的职位，处女座的美德也得到了一定的重视。\r\n", "record_count": 3859, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201606061619158MhYwyBuH1VvNW6s.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2014-09-02T07:37:47Z", "questions": [{"id": 74, "title": "处女座为什么这样红？", "content": "处女座为什么这样红？", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 660, "content": "因为处女座作出了风格，作出了水平", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161803PBls6pyuTGFNM3v4.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 661, "content": "忍不了处女座的人太多，吐槽的火力集中", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161803izq6IFv8hVef7rQp.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 662, "content": "人类喜欢跟风黑", "image": "img/option/option/201606061618030JfZqLWQRFBUwcNC.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 663, "content": "“我们处女座虽然有一些毛病，但是我们特棒”", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161804HrpPkzWBbmj3I5yd.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 664, "content": "处女座的陋习挺可爱的", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161804okOQzdaNYFfW2IHw.jpeg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 665, "content": "其他星座都面目模糊，只有处女座最亮", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161804x9oROb8W6G2TZEqp.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}